summary: 05/30/1993: An asylum-seeker's shelter in Cuxhaven was set on fire. German neighbors were suspected in the attack.
addnotes: This was one of a number of attacks on foreigners living in Germany and/or foreign-owned establishments, most employing arson as the attack type.
